The next likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), as the paper demonstrates the capabilities of the proposed models on AI tasks. The paper also mentions natural language semantics, which suggests cs.CL (Computation and Language) as another likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions using the models for image data, which suggests cs.CV (Computer Vision) as a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper uses modern optimization techniques, which suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible sub-category.
